Two fixes applied:

1. **s1 (omission)**: Added the empty-file check pattern between `getPart()` and `get(0)`:
   ```java
   if (partInfoList.isEmpty()) {
       throw new ApplicationException(
               MessageUtil.createMessage(MessageLevel.ERROR, "MSG00039"));
   }
   ```
   Also added `isEmpty`, `MessageUtil`, `空ファイルチェック` to the hints.

2. **s6 (section_issue)**: Removed the section entirely. The source element is only an RST anchor (`.. _`custom_tag_paging`:`) followed by a horizontal rule — a page boundary marker with no substantive content. Keeping it would mislead agents into expecting paging content in this file.

